snippet.title: Marvel Tokon: Fighting Souls - Official PS5 Closed Beta Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Don't miss the PS5 Closed Beta Announcement Trailer for Marvel Tokon: Fighting Souls, an upcoming action fighting game developed by ARC System Works. Players can take a dip into the wider Marvel Universe to duke it out in intense fighting battles with Marvel's biggest heroes, including Captain America, Ms. Marvel, Star-Lord, Iron Man, Storm, and Dr. Doom in an upcoming closed beta for the game. The closed beta will be fitted with 6 playable characters, online matches, spectator mode, training tutorial, and more. Marvel Tokon: Fighting Souls is coming soon to PlayStation 5 (PS5) and PC with a closed beta running from September 5 through September 7 exclusively on PlayStation 5 (PS5).

#MarvelTokonFightingSouls #Gaming #PS5

snippet.description:

Song: John Denver - Take Me Home, Country Roads (Lyrics)

Follow

 https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-cnCe5zradDZlcI8YZboBg?sub_confirmation=1&src=Linkfire&lId=357e202d-fff2-40c5-97b1-171bc915d19b&cId=d3d58fd7-4c47-11e6-9fd0-066c3e7a8751&sttick=0

Lyrics:

.Almost Heaven, West Virginia
Blue Ridge Mountains, Shenandoah River
Life is old there, older than the trees
Younger than the mountains, growing like a breeze

[Chorus]
Country roads, take me home
To the place I belong
West Virginia, mountain mama
Take me home, country roads
[Verse 2]
All my memories gather 'round her
Miner's lady, stranger to blue water
Dark and dusty, painted on the sky
Misty taste of moonshine, teardrop in my eye

[Chorus]
Country roads, take me home
To the place I belong
West Virginia, mountain mama
Take me home, country roads

[Bridge]
I hear her voice in the morning hour, she calls me
The radio reminds me of my home far away
Driving down the road, I get a feeling
That I should have been home yesterday, yesterday

[Chorus]
Country roads, take me home
To the place I belong
West Virginia, mountain mama
Take me home, country roads
Country roads, take me home
To the place I belong
West Virginia, mountain mama
Take me home, country roads
[Outro]
Take me home, (Down) country roads
Take me home, (Down) country roads
.........
